               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180218-2-cd7" type="crimeDate">20th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-2-off6 t18180218-2-cd7"></join>, fourteen wine glasses, value 7s.; one tumbler, value 6d.; one milk-pot, value 2d., and one piece of glass, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18180218-2-victim59" type="victimName">
                  Henry 
                  Cowley
               <interp inst="t18180218-2-victim59" type="surname" value="Cowley"></interp>
